x;\">上海赢家企业发展有限公司</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 27.4286px;\">，</span>是一家专注于金融领域教育与培训的平台型公司。以传播正确的<a href=\"http://www.10jrw.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(80, 139, 197); outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">金融投资</a>理念为己任，专注于投资者风险教育与知识传播。公司平台上有多个国内知名的投资培训类课程和训练平台。赢家教育作为<a href=\"http://www.10jrw.com/playback_94.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(80, 139, 197); outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">知行合一投资智慧</a>以及赢家操盘手特训营的课程承办方，相关课程已经在全国培训过超万名的投资者，平台培养出了数百名私募基金经理以及职业投资人。公司相关课程和训练平台深受广大投资者喜爱和好评，学员满意度超过99%。赢家教育秉承“知行合一、永续共赢”的企业经营理念，深耕细作，果敢进取，已经成为中国金融投资教育领域的排头兵和领军者</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 33px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.10jrw.com/data/upload/editer/image/2016/11/30/583e3bb55ef53.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 630px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 33px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: ba